{"tid":2234531,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：染武肺是「上帝祝福」　承諾免費為國民提供新藥　重提「是中國的錯，要付沉重代價」　","createTime":"2020-10-08T03:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T10:07:54.000Z","uid":66271,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"da30812975f1edd215b5572022756f44959c2649","tid":2234531,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/T_2IdqX_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FT_2IdqX_1200x0.png&h=d4223bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感染武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 留院 3 晚即出院的美國總統特朗普，首次回到橢圓形辦公室工作，並於辦公室外拍片，稱感染乃「上帝祝福」，因為讓他可以親身試到最新的治療方法，並承諾會為美國人免費提供自己曾接受的新藥。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說自己在染疫過程中未有感到嚴重不適，醫療團隊給他不同的藥物治療，他認為是藥廠 Regeneron 研發的藥物對他的康復至為關鍵，令他迅速感到身體好轉，他說另一家藥廠 Eli Lilly 亦有類似的藥物，他會授權生產及批准緊急使用，又承諾會為美國人民免費提供這些藥物，並不忘重提中國要為疫症擴散負責：<br />\n<br />\n「我現在站在白宮橢圓形辦公室外，這地方總是令人興奮。我想為你們（美國人民）爭取我接受的治療，我要令這些藥物免費提供給大家，你們毋須付出一分一毫，發生疫情不是你們的錯，是中國的錯，中國要會其對這國家所做的事付出沉重代價，中國要為對全球所做的事情付出沉重代價，大家記住這是中國的錯。」<br />\n<br />\n他又大讚新藥有神奇功效：「我入院時感到不適，但 （治療）24 小時內已經好轉，我想出院，...我想所有人都得到跟你們總統一樣的醫治，因為我覺得很好，簡直是完美。我認為這根本是上帝的祝福，包裝成讓我感染。我聽說過有這種藥，是我建議採用的，實在太棒了。我想，如果不是我，這藥就會有如其他藥一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n據美國約翰斯&middot;霍普金斯大學數據，現時美國已有 750 萬人確診，超過 21 萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gUbZ2PTKk3E&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgUbZ2PTKk3E%26feature%3Demb_title&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5LXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=d492e573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gUbZ2PTKk3E&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"3500729a17a09a385bf0fc5895ec91692df0f303","tid":2234531,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"支那既沉重代價同美國既沉重代價邊個重啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c3590408650f072fbd1faf0fcf5e3dc6b6b629","tid":2234531,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dab4003027c972bd7c561937c66750c46f2d33cf","tid":2234531,"uid":108266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c8f56d25c4e92595c747884619d22cc53d41af","tid":2234531,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df30c0a2f1e796c081785ba822c1a01d79603ae","tid":2234531,"uid":252993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"暫時未見到好沉重的代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe80a154185cea8bab7ac494376e760dec3d02f","tid":2234531,"uid":288803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"割香港賠償啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再拖累大中國"},{"pid":"2fa840dcb0cd3f8d8fa9377e9c24b3f511f777a7","tid":2234531,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3500729a17a09a385bf0fc5895ec91692df0f303","tid":2234531,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"支那既沉重代價同美國既沉重代價邊個重啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"支那吹水就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e560266b5c69e94b2c92edb5f906f17723dbed","tid":2234531,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":